    <title>个人主页搭建</title>
    <link href="https://talengu.github.io/2016/12/22/build_blog/"/>
    <id>https://talengu.github.io/2016/12/22/build_blog/</id>
    <published>2016-12-22T04:39:04.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-11-05T15:51:51.422Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>概要：<br>博客搭建的记录与分享，主要用了Hexo，NexT主题和Gitment评论系统。</p></blockquote><p>小技巧，在文章中使用<code>&lt;!-- more --&gt;</code>手动进行截断，Hexo 提供的方式。<br>下面就是用这个截断的～～<br><a id="more"></a></p><h2 id="安装Hexo"><a href="#安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo"></a>安装Hexo</h2><p><strong> Ubuntu16.04安装 </strong><br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ sudo apt install npm nodejs-legacy</div><div class="line">$ sudo npm install hexo-cli -g</div><div class="line">$ hexo init blog</div><div class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> blog</div><div class="line">$ npm install</div><div class="line">$ hexo server</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/" target="_blank" rel="external">Hexo中文网站</a></p><h2 id="安装NexT"><a href="#安装NexT" class="headerlink" title="安装NexT"></a>安装NexT</h2><p>按官网教程NexT安装，官网安装和配置教程比较好。<br><a href="http://theme-next.iissnan.com/getting-started.html" target="_blank" rel="external">http://theme-next.iissnan.com/getting-started.html</a></p><p>NexT的Github项目<br><a href="https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next" target="_blank" rel="external">https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next</a></p><p>NexT开发者的博客<br><a href="http://notes.iissnan.com" target="_blank" rel="external">http://notes.iissnan.com</a></p><h2 id="安装完的目录结构"><a href="#安装完的目录结构" class="headerlink" title="安装完的目录结构"></a>安装完的目录结构</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">.</div><div class="line">├── node_modules  <span class="comment"># nodejs的目录</span></div><div class="line">├── public        <span class="comment"># 输出网站目录</span></div><div class="line">├── scaffolds     <span class="comment"># hexo 的一些预设模版</span></div><div class="line">├── <span class="built_in">source</span>        <span class="comment"># 独立submodule</span></div><div class="line">├── themes        <span class="comment"># 主题 里面也有主题的配置文件不要与项目的配置文件搞混</span></div><div class="line">├── README.md</div><div class="line">├── _config.yml   <span class="comment"># 整个项目配置文件</span></div><div class="line">├── db.json</div><div class="line">├── index.html。  <span class="comment"># 用于跳转到public下</span></div><div class="line">└── package.json</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">5 directories, 5 files</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将source 文件夹作为一个submodule 用 <a href="https://git-scm.com/book/en/v2/Git-Tools-Submodules" target="_blank" rel="external">git submodule</a><br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment"># 对于我来说</span></div><div class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> path/to/your/github.io/project</div><div class="line">$ git submodule add https://github.com/talengu/blog_source <span class="built_in">source</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h2 id="在生成静态网站"><a href="#在生成静态网站" class="headerlink" title="在生成静态网站"></a>在生成静态网站</h2><p>下面操作都在 <code>path/to/your/github.io/project</code><br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment"># clone 项目</span></div><div class="line">$ git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/talengu/talengu.github.io</div><div class="line">$ git submodule init</div><div class="line">$ git submodule update</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># 切换到最新的submodule</span></div><div class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> <span class="built_in">source</span></div><div class="line">$ git merge origin/master</div><div class="line">$ git submodule update</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># 执行npm按照，由于已经生成它会按照package.json文件自动安装</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># 没有npm的话 安装 https://nodejs.org/en/download/</span></div><div class="line">$ npm install</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h2 id="我启用的配置"><a href="#我启用的配置" class="headerlink" title="我启用的配置"></a>我启用的配置</h2><p>Local Search</p><p>RSS</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装hexo-generator-feed</span></div><div class="line">npm install hexo-generator-feed --save</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># 在_config.yml 启用feed</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>MathJax<br>$\frac{d}{dx}c^n=nx^{n-1}$</p><p>Gitment 评论功能<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"># 安装gitment</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">$ npm install gitment --save</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">要修改theme/next 下文件参考：</div><div class="line">https://blog.csdn.net/yanzi1225627/article/details/77890414</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h2 id="图片"><a href="#图片" class="headerlink" title="图片"></a>图片</h2><ul><li>github上有项目图片就从项目中链接过来，比如头像就是我github的头像</li><li>重要的图片存在本项目中</li></ul><p>图标网站 <a href="http://fontawesome.io" target="_blank" rel="external">http://fontawesome.io</a> or <a href="https://www.easyicon.net/" target="_blank" rel="external">https://www.easyicon.net/</a></p><h2 id="编写规范"><a href="#编写规范" class="headerlink" title="编写规范"></a>编写规范</h2><p>以后再补充～</p><p>CopyLeft Here</p>]]></content>
    
